{"tid":2235060,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【選舉查數】周浩鼎申報逾百萬開支　報名日 4000 元向龍獅會僱 10 保安","createTime":"2020-10-08T11:09:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T11:20:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"afd0c7c1e8479eca671e3092ea983b3c9c9bc642","tid":2235060,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:09:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/選舉查數-周浩鼎申報逾百萬開支-報名日-4000-元向龍獅會僱-10-保安/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E6%9F%A5%E6%95%B8-%E5%91%A8%E6%B5%A9%E9%BC%8E%E7%94%B3%E5%A0%B1%E9%80%BE%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E9%96%8B%E6%94%AF-%E5%A0%B1%E5%90%8D%E6%97%A5-4000-%E5%85%83%E5%90%91%E9%BE%8D%E7%8D%85%E6%9C%83%E5%83%B1-10-%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%2F&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr9Rt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=61ba80f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E6%9F%A5%E6%95%B8-%E5%91%A8%E6%B5%A9%E9%BC%8E%E7%94%B3%E5%A0%B1%E9%80%BE%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E9%96%8B%E6%94%AF-%E5%A0%B1%E5%90%8D%E6%97%A5-4000-%E5%85%83%E5%90%91%E9%BE%8D%E7%8D%85%E6%9C%83%E5%83%B1-10-%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%2F&h=0137e1a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/選舉查數-周浩鼎申報逾百萬開支-報名日-4000-元向龍獅會僱-10-保安/</a><br />\n<br />\n政府將押後原定於今年九月舉行的立法會選舉，各候選人仍需申報選舉開支，政府將按申索指引發放補償。參選新界西的民建聯周浩鼎名單申報了逾 109 萬開支，當中花費 4 千元於報名日僱用十名保安，而服務由陳嘉輝龍獅總會提供，該會創辦人陳嘉輝，為新界社團聯會其中一名元朗區的特邀理事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/E89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202020-10-0520E4B88BE58D887.38.20_dFt8j_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FE89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202020-10-0520E4B88BE58D887.38.20_dFt8j_1200x0.png&h=f9ee91d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n周浩鼎於 7 月 22 日到海港政府大樓報名，同場有民建聯主席李慧琼、前主席兼全國人大常委譚耀宗、新界西立法會議員梁志祥現身支持。據開其支申報書，周浩鼎團隊及李慧琼團隊當日向陳嘉輝龍獅總會僱用了 10 名保安，每名 500 元，共涉及 5000 元，兩方再分攤有關開支，周浩鼎團隊付 8 成費用，即 4000 元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/chd_83Tqu_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fchd_83Tqu_1200x0.jpg&h=f5b137b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除周浩鼎，同是報名新界西競逐連任的何君堯，亦有以 6 萬元向陳嘉輝龍獅總會租借貨車作宣傳作用。該總會創辦人陳嘉輝為新界社團聯會其中一名元朗區的特邀理事，據《蘋果日報》報道，2013 年時任特首的梁振英及立法會議員梁志祥於天水圍舉辦論壇時，多名梁振英的支持者與示威者發生衝突，有示威者遭圍毆，而陳嘉輝有份帶領指罵及挑釁示威者。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》正向周浩鼎發訊息，以回應事件，仍待回覆。"},{"pid":"c5bc28d9db6abb6e3c19e02c7fc28d37f1d554dd","tid":2235060,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:11:18.000Z","msg":"400蚊請一個保安，咁低人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71155cb3981d90885acc7582ce6e1e92a3a9e039","tid":2235060,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5bc28d9db6abb6e3c19e02c7fc28d37f1d554dd","tid":2235060,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:11:18.000Z","msg":"400蚊請一個保安，咁低人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:11:39.000Z","msg":"原來係500"},{"pid":"59d4f22694a3ba526cb5fbc9cd8e7409010985d6","tid":2235060,"uid":184827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:11:48.000Z","msg":"政協黎添"},{"pid":"e614d0b91886c806b181c9b6179a799a71806a08","tid":2235060,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:20:21.000Z","msg":"龍獅會？ 反了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/51/Flag_of_Hong_Kong_%281959%E2%80%931997%29.svg/1200px-Flag_of_Hong_Kong_%281959%E2%80%931997%29.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F5%2F51%2FFlag_of_Hong_Kong_%25281959%25E2%2580%25931997%2529.svg%2F1200px-Flag_of_Hong_Kong_%25281959%25E2%2580%25931997%2529.svg.png&h=3fed12f2&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}